JOHANNESBURG - National Prosecuting Authority spokesperson Luvuyo Mfaku said on Tuesday the resignation of prosecutor Gerrie Nel had taken the NPA by surprise.The high-profile Nel announced on Tuesday afternoon that he was leaving the NPA to join lobby group AfriForum.eNCA reporter Karyn Maughan asked Mfaku if anyone had tried to talk Nel out of it. Watch the interview by clicking onthe video above.eNCA